# Architecture

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/core/VietnameseInput.ts` | DOM events, singleton, runtime API |
| `src/core/transform.ts` | Pure string transform — **no DOM** |
| `src/utils/helpers.ts` | Word extraction, vowel detection, `replaceText` |
| `src/constants.ts` | `INPUT_METHODS`, `VIETNAMESE_CHARS` |
| `src/types.ts` | Type definitions |
| `src/index.ts` | Public exports only |

## Rules

- Transform logic stays in `transform.ts` as pure functions (string in → string out)
- DOM/caret handling only in `VietnameseInput.ts` and `utils/helpers.ts`
- Re-export helpers via `src/utils/index.ts`
- Bind event handlers once in constructor
- Skip transform during `composition` events

## Style

- TypeScript strict; single quotes, semicolons, 80 cols (Prettier)
- No `console.log` (ESLint warns)
- `processInput` / `applyTone` are legacy shims — preserve if refactoring internals

## Common changes

| Task | Files |
|------|-------|
| Input method rules | `constants.ts` + `transform.test.ts` |
| Transform logic | `transform.ts` + `transform.test.ts` |
| Public API | `index.ts`, `VietnameseInput.ts`, `docs/api-reference.md` |
